  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. A supporting claim regarding construct stiffness predictive accuracy is included in the package; experimental evidence was gathered during bench testing but the formal derivation link from that evidence to the claim was inadvertently omitted during package assembly.",
